/2024/12/doechii@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/doechii">Doechii</a>分享了她所描述的新“节目”《<em>拒绝是一条河》</em>的预告片 - 请观看下面的视频。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/doechii-alligator-bites-never-heal-review-3788938">Doechii – “鳄鱼咬伤永远不会愈合”评论：关于斗争和韧性的坦率的声音日记</a></strong></li></ul><p>昨晚（12 月 26 日），这位说唱歌手在社交媒体上分享了<em>《拒绝是一条河</em>》的受<em>家庭事务</em>启发的预告片，该预告片将于 2025 年 1 月 2 日首播。除了预告片，由她本人和其他音乐家主演。</p><p>在预告片中，我们以 90 年代情景喜剧为灵感介绍了该节目的每位演员，尽管没有笑声。 <em>《Denial Is A River》</em>的主演还有 Zack Fox、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/schoolboy-q">ScHoolboy Q</a> 、Rickey Thompson、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/teezo-touchdown">Teezo Touchdown</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/earl-sweatshirt">Earl Sweatshirt</a> （饰演<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/brad-pitt">Brad Pitt</a> ）、H Wood、DJ Miss Milan、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/yung-baby-tate">Baby Tate</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sir">SiR</a> 。</p><p>观看下面的预告片。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">否认是一场河流表演| 2025 年 1 月 2 日首播<a href="https://t.co/OM8u2mtGSR">pic.twitter.com/OM8u2mtGSR</a></p><p> — 沼泽公主<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f40a.png" alt="🐊" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> （@officialdoechii） <a href="https://twitter.com/officialdoechii/status/1872412434264416399?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 12 月 26 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>目前尚不清楚预告片是否暗示了真实的演出或音乐视频，不过 Doechii 指示粉丝在 Instagram 上关注<a href="https://www.instagram.com/denialisarivershow/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">@DenialIsARiverShow</a> 。</p><p> “Denial Is A River”是她的混音带“Alligator Bites Never Heal”中最出色的曲目之一。早在 8 月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/doechii-alligator-bites-never-heal-review-3788938"><em>NME</em>就给予《Alligator Bites Never Heal》四颗星</a>，并写道：“Doechii 在这张专辑中深入探讨了细节，但到了最后，她找到了安慰和力量，让这张混音带感觉更像是一部声音日记。她的情感历程。”</p><p>自混音带发行以来，这位 Top Dawg Entertainment 的签约者已经达到了多个里程碑，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/doechii-announces-alligator-bites-never-heal-2024-world-tour-buy-tickets-3798354">进行一场门票售罄的世界巡演、</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-doechii-perform-with-sza-and-tyler-the-creator-at-camp-flog-gnaw-festival-2024-3813489">与 SZA 一起在 Camp Flog Gnaw 的主舞台上表演</a>，以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/katy-perry-teases-new-single-im-his-hes-mine-featuring-doechii-3793009">与 Katy Perry</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tyler-the-creator">Tyler, the Creator</a>合作他们各自的专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/katy-perry-143-review-3795535">“143”</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/tyler-the-creator-chromakopia-review-3807791">“Chromakopia”</a> 。 </p><figure id="attachment_3820435" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3820435" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3820435" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/doechii-@-2000x1270-Joe-Scarnici_Variety-via-Getty-Images.jpg" alt="Doechii 在 2024 年 Variety Hitmakers 早午餐会上接受“年度嘻哈颠覆者”奖。图片来源：Joe Scarnici/Variety via Getty Images" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/doechii-@-2000x1270-Joe-Scarnici_Variety-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/doechii-@-2000x1270-Joe-Scarnici_Variety-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/doechii-@-2000x1270-Joe-Scarnici_Variety-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/doechii-@-2000x1270-Joe-Scarnici_Variety-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/doechii-@-2000x1270-Joe-Scarnici_Variety-via-Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/doechii-@-200